  "identifier": "HB 621",
  "title": "AN ACT relating to class sizes for exceptional children and youth.",
  "abstract": "Amend KRS 157.220 to require the Kentucky Department of Education to promulgate administrative regulations in accordance with the maximum class sizes and caseloads specified for exceptional children and youth; make technical corrections; amend KRS 157.200 to define \"caseload\" and \"special classes\"; amend KRS 157.230, 157.3175, and 159.990 to conform.",
